54 684.0 m 558 684.0 l 0.5 w S
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 658.2 Td (Your Phone Is Your Biggest Distraction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630.4 Td (Your smartphone is the single most powerful tool for productivity or the single biggest) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.4 Td (source of distraction in your life. The difference comes down to how intentionally you set) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (it up. Most people use their phone on autopilot with default settings designed by) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (companies whose business model is to maximize your screen time.) Tj ET
