BT /F1 10 Tf 54 333.4 Td (Emails after purge: ___________) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 319.4 Td (Newsletters unsubscribed from: ___________) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 289.6 Td (Step 2: Unsubscribe Sprint) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 261.8 Td (Track every newsletter and promotional email you unsubscribe from:) Tj ET
