BT /F2 12 Tf 54 658.2 Td (Reclaiming Your Attention from Social Media) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630.4 Td (Social media platforms are engineered by teams of brilliant psychologists and engineers to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.4 Td (be as addictive as possible. They exploit our need for social validation, fear of missing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (out, and desire for novelty. The average person spends 2 hours and 27 minutes per day on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (social media, which adds up to over 37 days per year.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 564.6 Td (This is not about quitting social media entirely \(unless you want to\). It is about using) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 550.6 Td (it intentionally rather than compulsively, being a creator rather than a consumer, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 536.6 Td (ensuring these platforms serve your goals rather than stealing your time and mental) Tj ET
